  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President Ranil Wickremesinghe visits the Ministry of Defence",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe visited the Ministry of Defense located at the Sri Jayawardenepura Fort after taking the oath of office at the Parliament Complex on the 21st of Thursday morning.",
        "The President, who visited the Ministry, was received by Defense Secretary Retired General Kamal Gunaratna.",
        "This was President Ranil Wickremesinghe's first visit to a government institution after taking oath of office.",
        "During the President's visit, Minister Dron Alas, Attorney General, Secretary to the President, Acting Chief of Defense General General Shavendra Silva, Tri-Army Commanders, Inspector General of Police, Chief of State Intelligence and Director of National Intelligence were also present."
      ],
